Animal Shelter Managing System

1   must be able to track animals in shelter
2   must be able to track resources such as food and bedding
3   must be able to track adoption requests / applications
4   must allow data entry for the above information
5   must connect to server for multi-user
6   must allow user to manage database/website info within server
7   follow-up to above: need a website and database connection
8   must be accessible to non-tech literate users
9   must be able to synchronize with veterinatry database
10  must be able to aggregate data into appropriate readable/printable formats for physical printing
